<br />
Yep, thats the way we are on raids as well, but apparently that is a bit bugged.<br />
<br />
In Chardok last Saturday, one of my group members was able to loot a few items. I don't <i>think</i> the timer had run out, but it might have.<br />
<br />
In any event, it wasn't a problem, as he was also a guild member of mine. I just had him turn the stuff over to me before the raid ended, and we added it into the pool.<br />
<br />
We generally don't do open raids, so we rarely have that issue, even if someone does manage to loot out of turn.</font></p>
	
